dubstep.solution.plan

Class Projection

  • java.lang.Object
    • dubstep.solution.plan.Operator
      • dubstep.solution.plan.Operator.Unary
        • dubstep.solution.plan.Projection

  • public class Projection
extends Operator.Unary
    A concrete implementation of a relational plan operator representing a projection operator (technically projection and renaming operators rolled into one). A projection node contains a list of String, Expression pairs, defining the name and value of each column (respectively) produced by the projection operator.

      • getMapping

        public java.util.Map<Column,Expression> getMapping()
        Utility method to extract a translation between local variables applied over the columns in the output of this operator, and the expression that defines those operators. This is used by the optimizer to compose successive projection operators and to push selections in through projections.
